.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - the new flags for the ed command
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/creator/wiz_file_comm.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the current flags for the inbuild ed command.  THis
allows certain flag settings to be saved between sessions.
